1
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:24,180
♪The breeze of the 1990s drifts by♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:27,180
♪Memories slowly flicker past♪

3
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,430
♪My heartbeat
rises and falls with the tune♪

4
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,580
♪The story quietly begins here♪

5
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:38,640
♪Under the dim lights, our eyes meet♪

6
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,850
♪Time seems to stand still♪

7
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,990
♪Your smile
breaks through the clouds like sun♪

8
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:49,150
♪Melting the snow deep in my heart♪

9
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,090
♪Street posters spread signals of love♪

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:56,110
♪Our story slowly begins to ferment♪

11
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:00,730
♪Hand in hand,
going through every dusk corner♪

12
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:04,800
♪The taste of happiness is so subtle♪

13
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,740
♪Crossing back to the 1990s stage♪

14
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:12,480
♪You're my most beautiful surprise♪

15
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:16,210
♪Love's flame burns within my heart♪

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,710
♪Not afraid of obstacles ahead♪

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:23,560
♪Sway with the rhythm.
Feel your heart pound♪

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:27,150
♪This love will never change♪

19
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:35,080
♪We hold tight in this crazy era♪

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:40,060
♪1990s love is what we rely on♪

21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,937
=Episode 11=

23
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:46,480
Shanshan.

24
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:47,920
What are you doing?

25
00:01:51,475 --> 00:01:52,156
Shanshan.

26
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:53,400
Shanshan.

27
00:01:55,799 --> 00:01:57,200
Zhou Zeyang!

28
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:04,719
Shanshan.

29
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,560
Don't touch me.

30
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,040
Listen to my explanation, okay?

31
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:08,520
I saw it with my own eyes.

32
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,840
What is there left to explain?

33
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,599
You've fallen into their trap.

34
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:12,840
Think about it carefully.

35
00:02:13,919 --> 00:02:16,039
From the moment
Zhuang Yan came to your home,

36
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,879
hasn't she
been ruining our relationship,

37
00:02:19,159 --> 00:02:20,319
trying to make us break up?

38
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:23,159
Yan is against us being together,
but this has nothing to do...

39
00:02:23,159 --> 00:02:24,960
Shanshan, don't you get it yet?

40
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:27,000
She let you saw it on purpose,

41
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,825
just to split the two of us up.

42
00:02:29,650 --> 00:02:30,970
Even if that's true,

43
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,840
if you had nothing to do
with Qin Jiamin,

44
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,360
she wouldn't have had
the chance to let me see it.

45
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,400
How do you explain it?

46
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,719
How do I explain it?

47
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,039
How do I explain it?

48
00:02:45,637 --> 00:02:47,680
Qin Jiamin is Qin Mo's sister.

49
00:02:48,039 --> 00:02:49,000
If she gets upset,

50
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,439
I have to pack up and go.

51
00:02:50,439 --> 00:02:51,919
What can I say?

52
00:02:52,199 --> 00:02:54,039
What right do I have to refuse her?

53
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:54,960
Shanshan.

54
00:02:55,319 --> 00:02:57,319
I'm not like you people.

55
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,639
I, Zhou Zeyang, got where I am today

56
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:03,240
on my own.

57
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,120
Jinxin is my life!

58
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:07,262
Without Jinxin, I'm as good as dead!

59
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,800
Zeyang, I'm sorry.

60
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,039
I misunderstood you.

61
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:13,159
Shanshan,
don't believe everything he says.

62
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:15,800
Yan, Zeyang has it hard too.

63
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,560
(Jinxin Food)
He got where he is today step by step.

64
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,639
He doesn't really...

65
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:20,159
Don't touch me.

66
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:21,719
Zeyang.

67
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,039
Zeyang, are you okay?

68
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,159
I'm fine.

69
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,560
Ms. Zhuang

70
00:03:30,225 --> 00:03:32,706
didn't push me on purpose.

71
00:03:34,159 --> 00:03:35,360
What do you mean?

72
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,639
Are you saying I pushed you on purpose?

73
00:03:38,112 --> 00:03:39,792
My hand just lightly...

74
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,560
Enough!

75
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,479
A mild concussion.

76
00:03:49,762 --> 00:03:51,081
We're not sure about aftereffects.

77
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:52,360
Come with me to get the medicine.

78
00:03:52,375 --> 00:03:53,375
Okay, I'll go.

79
00:03:53,375 --> 00:03:54,535
Zeyang, lie down first.

80
00:03:57,437 --> 00:03:58,076
Ms. Zhuang.

81
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,759
I have no grudge against you.

82
00:04:00,919 --> 00:04:02,120
Why do you hate me so much?

83
00:04:07,425 --> 00:04:09,330
That box wouldn't have hit you at all.

84
00:04:09,662 --> 00:04:10,863
You did it on purpose.

85
00:04:11,325 --> 00:04:13,805
You staged this to drive a wedge
between me and Shanshan.

86
00:04:16,620 --> 00:04:17,240
Let me tell you.

87
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,519
My relationship with Shanshan

88
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,800
isn't as fragile as you think.

89
00:04:22,062 --> 00:04:24,120
That's just what you think.

90
00:04:24,439 --> 00:04:25,240
Ah.

91
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,199
Zeyang.

92
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:28,959
Are you alright?

93
00:04:28,959 --> 00:04:29,800
Ms. Zhuang.

94
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:32,319
Why do you keep doing this to me?

95
00:04:32,319 --> 00:04:33,720
No way, again?

96
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,800
Shanshan. He's pulling a pity act.

97
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,439
Get out.

98
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,737
A pity act.

99
00:04:38,737 --> 00:04:39,925
Yan, please leave.

100
00:04:44,312 --> 00:04:45,079
Are you okay?

101
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,000
Are you hurt?

102
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:53,639
I'm fine.

103
00:04:58,937 --> 00:04:59,737
Shanshan.

104
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,240
Some brown sugar water might help.

105
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,040
I'm just fired up from anger,

106
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,160
not catching a cold.

107
00:05:18,439 --> 00:05:19,720
Why drink brown sugar water?

108
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,439
Fired up?

109
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:22,199
Then I'll make you some green tea.

110
00:05:22,199 --> 00:05:23,240
Don't mention green tea.

111
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,319
It just makes me angrier.

112
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,600
Qin Mo.

113
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:32,439
Zhou Zeyang will be either
my brother-in-law

114
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:33,519
or your brother-in-law.

115
00:05:34,319 --> 00:05:35,160
Take a stance.

116
00:05:35,639 --> 00:05:36,920
Just think it through.

117
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:39,600
Whenever you want to tell Shanshan,

118
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,519
I'll support you.

119
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,360
I'll tell her.

120
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:43,639
I'll tell her now.

121
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:47,120
If she finds out later,
it'll probably hurt more.

122
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,040
She has the right to know.

123
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:54,279
Mo.

124
00:05:57,712 --> 00:05:58,249
Shanshan.

125
00:06:03,399 --> 00:06:05,399
Come here. We need to talk.

126
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,720
Perfect timing.

127
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:17,120
Zeyang proposed to me.

128
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:17,600
I said yes.

129
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,279
What?

130
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,560
How could you agree?

131
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,120
Who is he...

132
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,737
Did he buy a house?

133
00:06:22,737 --> 00:06:23,617
A car?

134
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,439
Is he prepared?

135
00:06:24,439 --> 00:06:25,399
And he proposed?

136
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,800
Love without money is fragile.

137
00:06:29,862 --> 00:06:30,817
I believe in Zeyang.

138
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,240
He'll give me a better life.

139
00:06:33,025 --> 00:06:33,920
Mo, I'm done talking.

140
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,920
I'm going to sleep.

141
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:40,319
Zhuang Yan.

142
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,839
Didn't you say you'd tell her?

143
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,160
It's obvious Zhou Zeyang

144
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,120
knew we'd expose him.

145
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,959
He acted first.

146
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:52,160
Judging from Shanshan's attitude,

147
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:54,199
she won't believe us.

148
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,040
It'd backfire instead.

149
00:06:56,319 --> 00:06:57,120
Then what do we do?

150
00:06:57,399 --> 00:06:58,560
Watch them get married?

151
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,399
No way.

152
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,399
As long as I'm breathing,

153
00:07:01,839 --> 00:07:04,240
I'll show Shanshan his true colors.

154
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,639
(Hard methods won't work.)

155
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:07,959
(We can only go soft.)

156
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,199
Shanshan.

157
00:07:19,837 --> 00:07:20,876
Why are you here?

158
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:26,920
I thought about it.

159
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:30,800
I shouldn't have treated
a patient like that.

160
00:07:31,187 --> 00:07:32,187
What's this?

161
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:34,000
A blood test report.

162
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,040
Oh.

163
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:37,560
Let me see.

164
00:07:41,175 --> 00:07:42,637
I wonder how he's doing.

165
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:46,720
Zhou Zeyang has AB blood type.

166
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,560
(What's going on?)

167
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:53,000
(My mom is type A.)

168
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,560
(Zhou Zeyang is type AB.)

169
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,319
(Then how did I get type O blood?)

170
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:10,879
Shanshan.

171
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,560
Mm?

172
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:16,800
You know I know some physiognomy.

173
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:19,650
Your forehead looks greenish lately.

174
00:08:20,300 --> 00:08:21,920
A sign of being fooled by bad men.

175
00:08:22,937 --> 00:08:24,177
No way, Yan.

176
00:08:24,177 --> 00:08:25,576
Zeyang wouldn't lie to me.

177
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:29,120
When it comes to metaphysics,

178
00:08:29,399 --> 00:08:30,639
better believe it

179
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:32,039
than not.

180
00:08:32,519 --> 00:08:33,639
Maybe this person

181
00:08:34,399 --> 00:08:35,440
hasn't appeared yet.

182
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:38,639
Yan, what are you talking about?

183
00:08:38,639 --> 00:08:40,440
All that metaphysics stuff is nonsense.

184
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,380
I'm done talking to you.

185
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,039
Shanshan.

186
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:45,200
You may

187
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:47,240
think everyone around you is good,

188
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:49,279
but fate never gets it wrong.

189
00:08:49,587 --> 00:08:51,720
Getting close to men brings misfortune.

190
00:08:52,159 --> 00:08:53,080
Just remember this.

191
00:08:53,559 --> 00:08:54,399
Men

192
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:55,262
are liars.

193
00:08:55,312 --> 00:08:56,360
Very few are any good.

194
00:08:56,575 --> 00:08:57,855
Why are they not good?

195
00:08:59,187 --> 00:09:00,387
I wasn't talking about you.

196
00:09:01,187 --> 00:09:02,187
But Mr. Qin,

197
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,519
here's a friendly reminder.

198
00:09:03,937 --> 00:09:06,000
Do more good deeds.

199
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,919
Don't ruin your reputation later.

200
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:11,840
Shanshan.

201
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:14,919
You don't know a single mom's pain yet.

202
00:09:15,919 --> 00:09:17,240
I've been through it.

203
00:09:17,399 --> 00:09:18,159
Learn from the past

204
00:09:18,159 --> 00:09:19,220
and avoid future mistakes.

205
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:20,840
You must stay clear-headed.

206
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:23,039
Even if you're not,

207
00:09:23,775 --> 00:09:24,685
use protection.

208
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:27,000
What protection?

209
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,580
What nonsense are you telling Shanshan?

210
00:09:29,399 --> 00:09:30,919
How is that nonsense?

211
00:09:31,350 --> 00:09:32,726
What's wrong with sex topics?

212
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,360
Are you lacking knowledge there?

213
00:09:34,925 --> 00:09:36,165
Want me to educate you?

214
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,039
Hey, come here.

215
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,159
Qin, there's soup in the pot.

216
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:39,420
Help me pour some and bring it over.

217
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,240
Oh.

218
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:41,840
Don't talk nonsense.

219
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:43,840
How is that nonsense?

220
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:44,720
This is science.

221
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,759
Yan.

222
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:47,600
He's never dated before.

223
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,679
Stop teasing him.

224
00:09:50,562 --> 00:09:51,712
Never dated?

225
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:55,960
Never dated

226
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,919
means it's the best time to learn these.

227
00:09:58,050 --> 00:10:00,799
Or he'll harm innocent women later.

228
00:10:01,837 --> 00:10:02,679
Yan.

229
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:05,639
Were you hurt in love before?

230
00:10:05,799 --> 00:10:07,312
Why so guarded against men?

231
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,440
About this darn love...

232
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,559
I never dated,

233
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,360
yet still suffered plenty from it.

234
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:18,320
And I'm not guarding against men.

235
00:10:18,530 --> 00:10:19,639
I'm guarding against this...

236
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:20,559
Yan, I... I'm done talking.

237
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:21,519
I need to bring Zeyang food.

238
00:10:21,519 --> 00:10:22,500
I'm running out of time.

239
00:10:22,559 --> 00:10:23,120
Huh?

240
00:10:23,159 --> 00:10:24,799
You haven't eaten yourself.

241
00:10:25,075 --> 00:10:26,423
No time. I'm not eating.

242
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,759
So who exactly is my dad?

243
00:10:35,262 --> 00:10:37,000
Based on my birth date,

244
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:39,000
the man who could be my dad

245
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,639
should've been by my mom's side.

246
00:10:41,919 --> 00:10:44,519
Who else but Zhou Zeyang?

247
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:45,360
Hey.

248
00:10:45,879 --> 00:10:46,799
Where's Shanshan?

249
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:52,399
Hey.

250
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:54,200
What's your blood type?

251
00:10:58,519 --> 00:11:00,039
What's your blood type?

252
00:11:00,662 --> 00:11:02,829
AB. Born August 16.

253
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,120
You're sure?

254
00:11:06,039 --> 00:11:07,600
I can't remember
my own blood type?

255
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,840
Why are you asking me this?

256
00:11:18,559 --> 00:11:20,120
To see if we're compatible.

257
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,519
(Thank goodness it's AB.)

258
00:11:27,759 --> 00:11:30,759
(If you were my real dad,
it'd be so cliche.)

259
00:11:32,825 --> 00:11:33,545
Compatible?

260
00:11:38,399 --> 00:11:39,039
Yes.

261
00:11:39,559 --> 00:11:41,100
A perfect match by fate.

262
00:11:44,337 --> 00:11:45,399
Then eat more.

263
00:11:49,399 --> 00:11:50,200
Jiamin.

264
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,262
You already proposed to Zhuang Shanshan.

265
00:11:51,262 --> 00:11:52,680
What else is there to say?

266
00:11:52,837 --> 00:11:54,350
You were playing me from the start.

267
00:11:54,350 --> 00:11:54,990
Jiamin.

268
00:11:55,519 --> 00:11:57,159
I truly like you.

269
00:11:57,840 --> 00:12:01,159
I was forced to marry her.

270
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,437
If you didn't want to propose,

271
00:12:03,437 --> 00:12:04,639
who could force you?

272
00:12:04,950 --> 00:12:06,360
It was Zhuang Yan.

273
00:12:06,525 --> 00:12:08,045
She got me injured

274
00:12:08,112 --> 00:12:09,512
and accused me of harming her.

275
00:12:09,512 --> 00:12:10,912
She had your brother fire me.

276
00:12:11,037 --> 00:12:12,840
Your brother
is completely charmed by her.

277
00:12:13,639 --> 00:12:14,879
I had no choice.

278
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:18,360
Shameless, despicable, disgusting.

279
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,399
Yes.

280
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,200
I did propose,

281
00:12:22,037 --> 00:12:23,919
but it was only a temporary measure.

282
00:12:24,637 --> 00:12:26,399
She didn't agree,

283
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:28,039
and I kept my job.

284
00:12:28,639 --> 00:12:30,399
Isn't that a win-win?

285
00:12:31,039 --> 00:12:31,960
Zhou Zeyang.

286
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:35,120
Do you think I'd believe these?

287
00:12:38,639 --> 00:12:40,799
What? Does it hurt again?

288
00:12:41,759 --> 00:12:43,399
How can she be so vicious?

289
00:12:43,559 --> 00:12:45,039
And are you a fool?

290
00:12:45,039 --> 00:12:47,799
Zhuang Shanshan
is just a parasite at my home.

291
00:12:48,212 --> 00:12:50,187
I'm my brother's birth sister.

292
00:12:50,487 --> 00:12:53,159
It's because you're Mr. Qin's sister

293
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:56,039
that I can't ask you for help.

294
00:12:56,662 --> 00:12:58,502
Qin Mo is your only family.

295
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:04,600
With Zhuang Yan and Zhuang Shanshan
in between,

296
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,960
you've suffered enough already.

297
00:13:08,399 --> 00:13:10,559
I can't burden you because of me.

298
00:13:12,250 --> 00:13:13,850
And I can't let you

299
00:13:14,725 --> 00:13:16,366
fall out with your brother.

300
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:20,440
What skillful gaslighting tactics.

301
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:21,759
Zeyang.

302
00:13:22,159 --> 00:13:23,000
I'm sorry.

303
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:26,480
I heard coworkers spreading rumors

304
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:28,320
about you proposing to Shanshan.

305
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:31,080
I was too upset
that I misunderstood you.

306
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:35,200
I didn't know you did this for me.

307
00:13:35,559 --> 00:13:38,519
I thought you just wanted to use me.

308
00:13:43,950 --> 00:13:44,751
Jiamin.

309
00:13:46,462 --> 00:13:48,143
You're the only person

310
00:13:48,799 --> 00:13:50,480
I've ever truly loved.

311
00:13:51,919 --> 00:13:52,720
Zhuang Shanshan

312
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:56,120
can't compare to you at all.

313
00:13:58,039 --> 00:13:58,840
Huh?

314
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:14,000
Who is it?

315
00:14:20,112 --> 00:14:20,912
Let's go.

316
00:14:25,799 --> 00:14:27,120
Who is it?

317
00:14:50,150 --> 00:14:53,788
♪The old dial tone circles in my ear♪

318
00:14:53,913 --> 00:14:57,225
♪Faded tickets point to a cicada summer♪

319
00:14:57,388 --> 00:15:00,975
♪The videotape
whispers your image in the frame♪

320
00:15:01,275 --> 00:15:04,563
♪Against the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smile♪

321
00:15:04,788 --> 00:15:08,413
♪I'm a clumsy guest in a frozen scene♪

322
00:15:08,575 --> 00:15:11,913
♪How do I answer familiar lines?♪

323
00:15:11,988 --> 00:15:15,700
♪I know
the train will leave this station♪

324
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:19,613
♪I know the ending's in a faded future♪

325
00:15:19,675 --> 00:15:25,725
♪Yet I want to approach that warmth♪

326
00:15:26,900 --> 00:15:33,638
♪Even one second rewrites missed lines♪

327
00:15:33,925 --> 00:15:38,200
♪Rewind to 1995,
back to the street we met♪

328
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:41,500
♪Wind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulder♪

329
00:15:41,575 --> 00:15:45,875
♪I wish I could pause and stop time♪

330
00:15:45,938 --> 00:15:49,588
♪Let unspoken love
be preserved forever as amber♪

331
00:15:49,588 --> 00:15:53,150
♪Rewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertips♪

332
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:56,463
♪Star sparks in your eyes burn my chest♪

333
00:15:56,463 --> 00:16:00,213
♪This looping script
is beyond my saving♪

334
00:16:00,213 --> 00:16:06,925
♪I can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglass♪
